alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/M2RSJ5e.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Bv8fK4b</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[novillyyy]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Biology is a mystery</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/WXSXUTh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zSFrxIJ.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/WXSXUTh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ThisBeMyUsername]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I’m not Steve Carell, I’m Michael Scarn.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CKYDZ36</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QN6J8Lu.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CKYDZ36</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BluesFish]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Just regular normal non suspicious memes v30</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4jJKVoG</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/B7Sl0Uu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Go home Stuart you are drunk</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xtmgeqp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is cute and inspiring and all but I’m feeling evil tonight so it’s not working. Hope it works for you.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bYk8rYp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My husband, everybody</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0tZudtZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Aaaaaand it’s me</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YOJjJ7q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sounds nice</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jWmi8hT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I see no issue here</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2WEgwrP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The series finale approaches….I just hope it’s not a Game of Thrones thing….</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZdOWJc4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I want to be included in all the weird nerd things!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/euCrQSI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>No idea what this is about</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hAzBTpk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Oh lord. It’s shrek all over again</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JNfbJs5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I got conned into buying lemonade from some neighbor kids and they were charging like $4 a cup and they had a card reader??? I had no excuse and then it was FUCKING MINUTE MAID I nearly threw it into a kids face</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kj7cavn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Omg that spider is so cute</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CcTPHY4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I don’t know why but this pic makes me laugh every time</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6fBzAEy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I can HEAR it</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZbTCNop.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Meeeeee</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lESZecK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Green is me. Also, in what universe is that fox green?!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AlSohkA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Literally all that bitch had to do was shut her mouth forever and fuck off into the sunset. Why.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6NGfU6q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>But what about the guys who like big dicks in their mouths</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/J4vcenz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I sent this to someone I know who’s a KFC executive but he says they won’t sell them</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e1QS5R7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Besties, would you rather a) let a dude know he has disappointed you and make him do the job right or b) fake an orgasm and just get outta there? No wrong answers.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2T7wBsm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>More memes I sent to my KFC guy that he ignored</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PirohOC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>There’s no wrong path my friend, everyone has their purpose, mine is just stabbin peeps</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XNG9nVg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>There’s like a 90% chance I’d either die or want to die</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/w9idLZZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Life IS weird but so am I!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xV0ZwAK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I don’t have my glasses on so for all I know it could be a kiwi. Or cake.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PqWf2ow.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’s me I’m a feral hoe</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xiIP9Bh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Meh</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QnItu0H.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Give a bunch of monkeys enough time with a typewriter and eventually they’ll reinvent Shakespeare…. Nah tumblr is just the Wild West of weird and it fucking acts like it</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tCDuHy7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sigh.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ThISPQX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Is there a way to do this with an entire relationship? Just abort mission when it gets too awkward?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0x4hzex.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yep. A nice lovely blend of proteins, fats, and carbs.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nN7ze0z.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is the most Texas thing I’ve ever seen, except Whataburger didn’t make it</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KC0i2s9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The chaos gremlin in me would uninvite Grandma just to see what happens</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3US6Vgn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I actually just busted out my favorite toys to give to my baby. They’re Barbie’s and he’s a boy but no one cares except my mom and she’s had it too easy for too li</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SoIxkfI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I know fang bangers are convenient but god at what cost</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IBh6wUC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Life gets a lot simpler when you’re whatever kind of autistic I am where everyone ends up fucking hating you. It’s just a matter of time before they get upset with you so you just do your thing without regards to their stupid neurotypical feelings that make no sense</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YRwQgob.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Dragon!!!!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/z5X17gG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And both are ridiculously easy!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4K4L65M.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Make sure to balance human flesh with vegetables and fish to avoid getting the shakes</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/msW50hQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I think this is an ad but it amused me</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dinkbpJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’s weird being this good at something I utterly loathe. Like my brains default is “jump off a bridge and die” and yet I have that dumbass part of it trussed up and full of bear tranqs in the back while the rest of me is having a blast</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lhlgxCX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I really like this quote. Also “I love you on purpose” - Casey McQuiston. RED WHITE AND ROYAL BLUE is so damn good</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/D4ZMn2c.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>What in the goddamn fuck is our world</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2Vh9NDC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I would pay so much money for one of these. The stupid one I got was digital and fuckin erased itself after a few days.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MmAqi0A.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sounds gay im in</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xjVCfT4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>No. No they are not. Probably idk</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CzQCHfd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I need an escape hatch for when I’ve overestimated my social abilities</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2JEnmpU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Doggie tax! 

I usually tell a story so ummmmmm last night the baby was very fussy and so I passed him off to my husband bc I’ve been sick and he’s had it too easy lately and I heard them watching animal videos on YouTube and my husband is just chattering away and then he gets desperate I guess and goes “do you know the tale of darth plagius the wise?” And then PROCEEDS TO FUCKING BUTCHER THE SPEECH I am seriously considering divorce I don’t even like the prequels and I still know it by heart he is embarrassing the family and setting a bad example for my son</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4jJKVoG</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[kirbyvictorious]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A House of My Own</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Q2OILte</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8gYCuXX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Q2OILte</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[dontpassmeby]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>More Russian Warcrimes</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ibFhsrE</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FzLP2mv.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MON-90</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uiElSmo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Tripwire attached to grenade pin. Self-explanatory.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TX7GZZS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Nailbomb in what seems to be a beercan.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TbQjM4q.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>What is it with Russians and washing machines?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/F5sp9QE.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hDaatX8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Tripwire attached to grenade pin. Again, self-explanatory.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1fdpLNB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>More tripwires</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2sdrth3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Grenade pin secured to left door, grenade secured to right door. Pin is pulled when either door is opened.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9gCFq9H.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/alRIEEY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LV4G5gP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Pull pin from grenade and put it in a glass.

I guess the intent here is for the glass to fall out of the cupboard when the door is opened, resulting in a detonation.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QhF2G5P.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Grenade in a can inside a washing machine. Lift can, grenade falls out resulting in a detonation.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Kkq1PbY.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I don't have words to describe these animals. I really don't...

The booby traps you see here aren't directed at the Ukranian military, but at Ukranian civilians, by defeated, retreating Russian forces. Burn in hell, every last one.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ibFhsrE</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ADegenFromUpcountry]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I scoff at them</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/AGCuqpp</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ojgl0iA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/AGCuqpp</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CeleryMan7]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>This is how to stop your wife shopping.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/HQjyT7W</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JmD6lvE.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/HQjyT7W</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[JaSphere1111]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Touch da beef</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/wNDFKtA</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qO63YnJ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/wNDFKtA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[RazorSizzleBoopleSnoot]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Don't be kicking my cab, mkay...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ExrFTDH</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ut78YcJ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ExrFTDH</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[rhuala]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>On point</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/LqDpyV8</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9DV5nXN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/LqDpyV8